description-'Set of 7 watches; assigned by Hundertwasser tot he 7 days of creation APA 327   937 B     The First Day         edition of 4,991 APA 19     138 A     The Second Day    edition of 4,992 APA 322   936 A     The Third Day        edition of 4,993 APA 264   894 C     The Fourth Day      edition of 4,994 APA 36     218 A     The Fifth Day         edition of 3,995 APA 16     134 G     The Sixth Day       edition of 2,996 APA 143   767 A      The Seventh Day   edition of 1,997 Swiss quartz clockwork technology Developed in collaboration with L-Scheybal, LAKS WATCH, Vienna',
